          </div>

          <!-- ── CP detail card (overlay reveals this) ── -->
          <div class="cp-detail-expand" id="cp-detail-top">
            <div class="cpd-inner">
              <p class="cpd-intro">Every skill writes a JSON checkpoint after each state change. Single source of truth — any skill can read any other's to rebuild context. Plain JSON on disk · no database · no vendor lock-in.</p>
              <div class="cpd-json">
                &#123;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">"skill"</span>: <span class="s">"oc-app-architect"</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">"phase"</span>: <span class="s">"build"</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">"progress_table"</span>: &#123; <span class="s">"discover"</span>: <span class="s">"complete"</span>, <span class="s">"spec"</span>: <span class="s">"in_progress"</span> &#125;,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">"context_primer"</span>: <span class="s">"2-sentence summary..."</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">"blockers"</span>: [<span class="s">"waiting on API key"</span>],<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">"next_actions"</span>: [<span class="s">"/oc-git-sync"</span>],<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">"cost"</span>: &#123; <span class="k">"total_usd"</span>: 1.81 &#125;,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">"eval_scores"</span>: [&#123; <span class="k">"rubric"</span>: <span class="s">"oc-bug-check"</span>, <span class="k">"score"</span>: 0.86 &#125;],<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">"telemetry_handle"</span>: &#123; <span class="k">"enabled"</span>: false &#125; <span style="color:var(--inst)">&#47;&#47; v1.6 wire 1.1 (additive)</span><br>
                &#125;
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- ── Orchestrator → 6 checkpoint sync diagram (clockwise build animation) ── -->
