            <div class="cpd-inner">
              <p class="cpd-intro">The oc-orchestrator routes every skill invocation across projects. Tracks which checkpoint is current, enforces audit gates before deploys, and answers <code>/oc-ops</code> queries. Reads all 29 checkpoints; writes its own pipeline state.</p>
              <svg class="orch-route-svg" viewBox="0 0 720 200" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Orchestrator routing decision: oc-app-architect checkpoint update routed to oc-ux-engineer, oc-dash-forge, and oc-api-dev in parallel">
                <defs>
